@abstract class_name BallisticSolutions extends Object


## Library for calculating interception times, impact positions, and firing vectors,
## taking into account the velocities and accelerations of both projectile and target.
##
## [BsTime] - Provides methods for computing interception times. [br]
## [BsPosition] - Provides methods for computing impact positions and displacement. [br]
## [BsVelocity] - Provides methods for computing required firing velocities. [br]
## [br]
## [BsSolution2D] / [BsSolution3D] / [BsSolution4D] - Returns all information in one call. [br]
## [br]
## [BsEquations] - Provides core ballistic equations. [br]
## [BsVectorExtensions] - Extensions for [Vector2], [Vector3], [Vector4].
##
## @tutorial(Ballistic Solutions): https://github.com/neclor/ballistic-solutions/blob/main/README.md
